r4816 | andrius | 2017-01-26 16:14:38 +0200 (Thu, 26 Jan 2017) | 6 lines

trunk/
Canonicalizing CIF data item names in a bunch of scipts that have not used
this feature before. Homogenuous treatment of CIF data item names in the
whole system is neccessary both to leverage the reusability of code and to
avoid bugs.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
