------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4768 | andrius | 2016-11-03 12:59:28 +0200 (Thu, 03 Nov 2016) | 6 lines

trunk/
Bugfix: ceasing to exclude "comments" (all lines starting with '#',
optionally with leading space) from the output of cif_split_primitive,
since such behaviour may destroy data, the most obvious example being
comment lines included in CIF text fields.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4764 | andrius | 2016-10-29 15:14:33 +0300 (Sat, 29 Oct 2016) | 6 lines

trunk/
Bugfix: escaping newline characters in messages, generated by
COD::UserMessage, via numeric character reference '&#10;' in order to
comply with the EBNF grammar of error messages as published in
Merkys et al. 2016.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
