r4428 | andrius | 2015-12-10 12:08:21 +0200 (Thu, 10 Dec 2015) | 7 lines

trunk/
Fixing a bug in setting planarity value in
COD::AtomNeighbours::from_chemistry_mol(): instead of setting boolean
value for 'is_planar' key, a value for 'planarity' is set to 0, thus
whatever the flat planarity threshold is used, such atom is treated as
planar.

