r4406 | antanas | 2015-12-08 08:46:09 +0200 (Tue, 08 Dec 2015) | 4 lines

cod-tools/ (antanas@echidna.ibt.lt)
Enhancement: adding the ' -- fixed' suffix to the CIF parser warning 
